OL,3,CMother found guilty over deaths of
OL,4,Cfour boys in London house fire
OL,6,FDeveca Rose, who left her two sets of
OL,7,Ftwins in a locked terrace, has been
OL,8,Ffound guilty over their deaths, as Amy
OL,9,FLewis reports
OL,11,FA woman was found guilty on Thursday
OL,12,Fover the deaths of her four young sons
OL,13,Fin a fire after she left them home
OL,14,Falone to go to Sainsbury's.
OL,16,FDeveca Rose had left her two sets of
OL,17,Ftwins in her locked terraced house in
OL,18,Fsouth-west London when the fatal blaze
OL,19,Fbroke out on the evening of December
OL,20,F16, 2021.
