OL,3,CMother found guilty over deaths of
OL,4,Cfour boys in London house fire
OL,6,FThe 30-year-old defendant, who had
OL,7,Fsplit up with her partner and suffered
OL,8,Ffrom mental health problems, was
OL,9,Fcharged with four counts of
OL,10,Fmanslaughter. She had denied the
OL,11,Fcharges.
OL,13,FJudge Mark Lucraft KC said it was a
OL,14,F"tragic case" as he adjourned
OL,15,Fsentencing to November 15 and granted
OL,16,FRose continued bail.
OL,18,FThe family had been living in squalor,
OL,19,Fsurrounded by rubbish and human
OL,20,Fexcrement, before the tragedy.
