OL,6,FProsecutor Kate Lumsdon KC had told
OL,7,Fthe court: "There was rubbish thickly
OL,8,Fspread throughout the house. The
OL,9,Ftoilet and the bath were full of
OL,10,Frubbish and could not be used.
OL,12,FBuckets and pots were used as toilets
OL,13,Finstead.
OL,15,F"Rose had gone to the supermarket,
OL,16,Fleaving Leyton and Logan Hoath, aged
OL,17,Fthree, and four-year-olds Kyson and
OL,18,FBryson Hoath at the rented home in
OL,19,FSutton
