OL,3,CMother found guilty over deaths of
OL,4,Cfour boys in London house fire
OL,6,F"When a cigarette or tea light in the
OL,7,Fliving room sparked a fire, the boys
OL,8,Fwere trapped and ran upstairs calling
OL,9,Ffor help.
OL,11,F"A neighbour tried to break down the
OL,12,Ffront door before firefighters in
OL,13,Fbreathing apparatus went in and found
OL,14,Fthe children's bodies under beds."
OL,16,FThey children were rushed to two
OL,17,Fseparate hospitals but attempts to
OL,18,Fsave them failed and they later died
OL,19,Ffrom inhalation of fire fumes.
