OL,3,CMother found guilty over deaths of
OL,4,Cfour boys in London house fire
OL,6,FWhen Rose came home, she claimed she
OL,7,Fleft the children with a friend, which
OL,8,Fprompted firefighters to go back into
OL,9,Fthe house to search for her.
OL,11,FPolice carried out extensive inquiries
OL,12,Fto find Jade and concluded she either
OL,13,Fdid not exist or had not been at the
OL,14,Fhouse that day.
OL,16,FIn police interviews, Rose admitted
OL,17,Fleaving the boys alone in the house on
OL,18,Ftwo earlier occasions.
