OL,4,Cfour boys in London house fire
OL,6,FThe children's father, Dalton Hoath,
OL,7,Fsaid in a statement that she had left
OL,8,Fthem alone once or twice to go to the
OL,9,Fnearby shop before.
OL,11,FMr Hoath, who had split up with the
OL,12,Fdefendant, added that he was
OL,13,F"devastated" and his world had been
OL,14,Fturned "upside down" by the loss of
OL,15,Fhis "young, boisterous lads".
