OL,3,CMother found guilty over deaths of
OL,4,Cfour boys in London house fire
OL,6,FPaternal great-grandmother Sally
OL,7,FJohnson said: "I was aware that she
OL,8,Fwould leave the boys by themselves in
OL,9,Fthe house. When I asked her about
OL,10,Fthis, she would say: 'Oh no, I just
OL,11,Fwent to the pop shop', which is a
OL,12,Flocal shop just seven houses away.
OL,14,F"I do not know how often this happened
OL,15,Fbut I remember several times I phoned
OL,16,Fthe house and Kyson answered the phone
OL,17,Fand told me 'Mummy has gone to the pop
OL,18,Fshop'."
