OL,4,Cfour boys in London house fire
OL,6,FPaternal step-grandmother Kerrie Hoath
OL,7,Fdescribed the boys as "polite,
OL,8,Fcarefree and very much loved" but
OL,9,Frecalled Rose not allowing her into
OL,10,Fthe house.
OL,12,FOn one occasion she dropped the boys
OL,13,Fhome and asked to use the toilet, only
OL,14,Fto be told by Rose: "No, there is a
OL,15,FTesco down the road, you can go
OL,16,Fthere", the court heard.
