OL,6,FMrs Hoath said: "The atmosphere was
OL,7,Falways tense when I was there. It was
OL,8,Flike Deveca did not want me to be
OL,9,Fthere."
OL,11,FJurors were told that social worker
OL,12,FGeorgia Singh had raised concerns
OL,13,Fabout the family but the case was
OL,14,Fclosed three months before the fire.
