OL,6,FCross-examining, defence barrister
OL,7,FLaurie-Anne Power KC said: "You have
OL,8,Fgot a decline in her physical
OL,9,Fappearance, a decline in the way she
OL,10,Fis looking after herself, a decline in
OL,11,Fher mental health, dissociating with
OL,12,Fher children with her.
OL,14,F"She's telling you that's likely to
OL,15,Fcontinue and she has point-blank
OL,16,Frefused to let you see the children.
OL,17,FThese are all alarm bells when you
OL,18,Fthink about family intervention.
