OL,6,F"It was not your decision to close the
OL,7,Fcase but the reason you set out the
OL,8,Fconcerns was because you yourself had
OL,9,Fthose concern about Ms Rose and the
OL,10,Fboys."
OL,12,FMs Singh agreed but told jurors she
OL,13,Fbelieved her concerns had been dealt
OL,14,Fwith by another social worker who had
OL,15,Fgone round later the same day as her
OL,16,Flast visit in July 2021.
OL,18,FPreviously a health visitor had raised
OL,19,Fconcerns about the family but they
OL,20,Fwere not followed up after she
OL,21,Fretired, jurors were told.
