OL,6,FThe children had not attended school
OL,7,Ffor three weeks before their deaths.
OL,9,FRose attended much of the trial by
OL,10,Fvideo-link from home on medical advice
OL,11,Fand declined to give evidence in her
OL,12,Fdefence.
OL,14,FThe court heard there was evidence
OL,15,Fsuggesting she was probably depressed
OL,16,Fand may have suffered from a
OL,17,Fpersonality disorder, but the
OL,18,Fprosecution asserted that was not a
OL,19,Fdefence.
